      <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M20.59 13.41l-7.17 7.17a2 2 0 01-2.83 0L2 12V2h10l8.59 8.59a2 2 0 010 2.82z"/><circle cx="7" cy="7" r="1.5"/></svg>
      <span>40% bulk discount active — Add 72 more to save 50%</span>
